reviewText: This is a home movie of a guy doing a barely adequate job of demonstrating kata. He's hard to listen to.

SORRY TO SAY IT BUT TIS "TRUTH!" ...BUT FOR ME!!!!...THE ATTEMPT WAS WEAK,DISSAPOINTING & BORING!  ...THE SENSEI SEEMED TO BE LACKING IN ENERGY & SPIRIT!!!  ...WAS THIS OLD MAN JAKE OF ALL TRADES AWAKE OR SLEEP WALKING????  ...WHERE IS THE "WARRIOR????"..."WOOOOW!!"
